---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Warranty" description="Klovo's 10-year warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship. Learn about coverage details and how to make a claim.">

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="text-klovo-amber font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Warranty</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">10 years. Because we mean it.</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-10">
            Every Klovo cabinet is backed by our 10-year limited warranty. We build our cabinets to last decades — and we put our money where our mouth is.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8 reveal">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">What's Covered</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
              Our warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship under normal residential use. This includes panel integrity, connector function, hinge mechanisms, and drawer slides.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">What's Not Covered</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
              Normal wear and tear, damage from misuse, commercial use, unauthorized modifications, and damage from exposure to standing water. Our cabinets are moisture-resistant, not waterproof.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">How to Make a Claim</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
              Contact us at <a href="mailto:warranty@klovo.com" class="text-klovo-blue hover:text-klovo-blue-dark">warranty@klovo.com</a> with your order number, photos of the issue, and a brief description. Our team will respond within 2 business days.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-warm-neutral rounded-lg reveal">
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            For full warranty terms and conditions, please contact our support team. Warranty is valid for the original purchaser and begins on the date of purchase. Proof of purchase required for all claims.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
